        "@value": "<p>Your community talent on display. Join us when Sheeptown Players Drama Society celebrates the 20th anniversary of 'Fort's Got Talent'.  Your favourite community talent show returns celebrating the abilities of your local stars in one special night on stage at the Shell Theatre. Music, dance, comedy and more... certainly something for everyone in this great show!</p>\n\n\n<style>\n@media screen and (max-width: 600px){iframe{width:100%;}}\n.location-page-temp {display: block!important;}\n</style>"
