        "@value": "A Broadsway Christmas"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>Celebrate the season with JUNO‑nominated vocalist and JAZZ‑FM91 host Heather Bambrick and Dora Award-nominated pianist Diane Leah, and their stellar 6‑piece band. Together they reimagine holiday classics and uncover unexpected seasonal gems with delightful humour, inventive arrangements and effortless musicality. Get into the seasonal spirit with the glow of a late‑night jazz lounge, complete with enchanting music, delightful stories and the unmistakable 'Broadsway' touch.</p>\n \n<p>Part of the Discover Your Stage 2026 - 2027 Series at 19 on the Park Theatre</p>"
