    ],
    "http://schema.org/url": [
      {
        "@id": "https://ww2.ticketpro.ca/event.php?event_id=7671"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "A Re-Creation of the Johnny Cash Christmas Special"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "\n<p>Step back in time and celebrate the spirit of the holidays with 'A Re-Creation of the Johnny\nCash Christmas Special.' This heartwarming live concert event captures the magic and charm\nof the legendary television specials hosted by Johnny Cash in the late 1960s and early 1970s.\nStarring Canada's leading Johnny Cash tribute artist, this authentic production brings The Man\nin Black's timeless music and storytelling to life with beloved hits and holiday favorites that echo\nthe warmth and spirit of his iconic TV specials.</p>\n<p>Just like the original broadcasts, the evening also features special guest tributes to some of the\nera's most celebrated stars. Audiences will enjoy unforgettable performances honoring Roy\nOrbison, Anne Murray, Roy Clark, and Crystal Gayle—recreating the excitement of the guest\nappearances that made the Johnny Cash Christmas Special a television classic.</p>\n<p>Blending classic country, rockabilly, and holiday cheer, 'A Re-Creation of the Johnny Cash\nChristmas Special' is a nostalgic journey filled with great music, heartfelt moments, and the\ntimeless songs that defined an unforgettable era. Perfect for the holiday season, this show will\nhave audiences tapping their toes, singing along, and filled with Christmas spirit.</p>\n\n"
      }
    ],
