    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Alex Cuba"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>It's a strange thing, watching audiences sing along with Alex without speaking his native Spanish. But they do.</p>\n\n<p>They 'la-la-la' their way from chorus to chorus, caught up in his inescapable gravitational pull. His warm, elastic vocals float above a sound essentially from everywhere-an effortless mix of Funk, Soul, and pan-Latin textures-and no matter where you're from, you can't help it. You're home. 'la-la-la' with us in a special night with this multi-Juno award, and Grammy award winner.</p>\n\n<p><a href='https://alexcuba.com/' target='_blank'>alexcuba.com</a></p>\n\n<iframe width='560' height='315' src='https://www.youtube.com/embed/98aYCT6Ife4?si=KXJkJQeSNYK-DImA' title='YouTube video player' frameborder='0' allow='accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share' referrerpolicy='strict-origin-when-cross-origin' allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<iframe width='560' height='315' src='https://www.youtube.com/embed/Cz_C_sRXysE?si=3hiH59GsCsXdT5Fn' title='YouTube video player' frameborder='0' allow='accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share' referrerpolicy='strict-origin-when-cross-origin' allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<iframe width='560' height='315' src='https://www.youtube.com/embed/wdAykSHOCEM?si=2KdbSq75mKLgLeOe' title='YouTube video player' frameborder='0' allow='accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share' referrerpolicy='strict-origin-when-cross-origin' allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<style>\n@media screen and (max-width: 600px){iframe{width:100%;}}\n.location-page-temp {display: block!important;}\n</style>"
      }
