    ],
    "http://schema.org/url": [
      {
        "@id": "https://ww2.ticketpro.ca/event.php?event_id=7756"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Canvas and Creativity: Summer Paint Night"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p><b>Spread Your Wings: Summer Paint Night at Five Points Theatre</b></p>\n\n<p>Escape the summer heat and step into a world of color! Join us for an enchanting evening of creativity, community, and relaxation for our Summer Paint Night: Butterfly Edition.<br>\nWhether you are a seasoned artist or have never picked up a paintbrush in your life, this event is designed for everyone. <br>\nOur instructor will guide you step-by-step through creating a vibrant, beautiful butterfly that captures the summer spirit.</p>\n\n<p><b>All Supplies Provided:</b> We will hand you a canvas, brushes, paints, and an apron. Just bring your creativity!<br>\n<b>Step-by-Step Guidance:</b> Our art instructor will lead the way, helping you bring your unique butterfly canvas to life <br>\n<b>A Vibrant Atmosphere:</b> Enjoy great music, a lively venue, and a fully licensed bar with snacks, seasonal drinks and refreshments available for purchase.<br>\n<b>Take-Home Art:</b> A finished 16x20 inch canvas masterpiece created entirely by you.</p>\n\n<p><b>Spaces are limited to ensure a comfortable experience for everyone, so grab your friends, secure your tickets, and let's make some magic happen!</b></p>\n\n\n\n\n<style>\n@media screen and (max-width: 600px){\niframe{width:100%;}\n}\n</style>\n\n"
      }
    ],
