    ],
    "http://schema.org/url": [
      {
        "@id": "https://ww2.ticketpro.ca/event.php?event_id=7569"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Chilliwack"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>Come sing along to the songs you love! 'Fly At Night', 'California Girl', 'My Girl (Gone Gone Gone)', 'Lonesome Mary', 'Whatcha Gonna Do', and more. Join Legendary Canadian rock band Chilliwack for an evening of music & memories as they hit the road for the last time in their 55-year history.</p>\n\n<p>As one fan said recently, 'They sounded exactly the same, I couldn't believe it! The energy, the high notes, all the good songs. Sooooo worth it!' - Robert C. 2025</p>\n\n<p>The band has produced 12 albums, numerous hits, and received 15 gold and platinum albums making them one of the Greatest Canadian bands of all time. Their live album 'There and Back' continues to win over a whole new generation of fans, showcasing Chilliwack's dynamic and electrifying live performances of the hit songs we all know and love.</p>\n\n<p>Come join in the fun before this farewell tour is gone, gone, gone.</p>\n\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {display: block!important;}\n@media screen and (max-width: 600px){iframe{width:100%;}}\n</style>\n"
      }
    ],
