    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>Step into the world of velvet voices and swinging rhythms with Crooner Kings: A Night of Timeless Melodies, a captivating theatre experience celebrating the songs made famous by the great crooners. This show pays tribute to iconic artists like Frank Sinatra, Dean Martin, Nat King Cole, Tony Bennett, and Michael Bublé, and many others—bringing their legendary tunes to life in an evening of unforgettable music.</p>\n\n<p>At the heart of Crooner Kings are two accomplished vocalists, each bringing their own unique flair to the stage.</p>\n\n<p>Andrew Martin is from Toronto, Ont. He has captivated audiences all over the world with his powerful voice and magnetic stage presence.</p>\n\n<p>Angel Saucedo is from Los Angeles, CA. This 21-year-old male vocalist is quickly making his mark as a modern crooner with a passion for timeless melodies. Fluent in both English and Spanish, he captivates audiences with his versatile voice, easily transitioning between languages and genres.</p>\n\n<p>Their styles capture the essence of the crooning tradition while offering fresh interpretations of beloved standards. Whether you're nostalgic for the Rat Pack era or discovering these gems for the first time, the interplay between the performers promises to delight audiences of all ages.</p>\n\n<p>This is a show for all ages catering to both lifelong fans and newcomers. Crooner Kings is a celebration of timeless melodies, stylish harmonies, and the enduring allure of classic vocal music. With witty banter, captivating duets, and solo performances that spotlight each singer's individual strengths, the show guarantees a night of entertainment, nostalgia, and pure joy.</p>\n\n<p>Don your best evening attire, gather your friends, and let the Crooner Kings serenade you with the very best of the great crooners—performed by two of today's most talented vocalists.</p>\n\n\n<style>\n@media screen and (max-width: 600px){\niframe{width:100%;}\n}\n</style>"
