    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "DARK GOTHIC Candlelit Experience - Halloween Edition"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>Step into a hauntingly beautiful world where music and candlelight create an unforgettable gothic atmosphere.</p>\n\n<p>On November 3 at 6:00 PM, the stunning Carleton Dominion-Chalmers Centre (Ottawa) will be transformed into a dark, immersive space illuminated by hundreds of candles. An outstanding string quartet will bring to life iconic and mysterious soundtracks in a unique, cinematic experience.</p>\n\n<p>Program: Wednesday, Stranger Things (dark pieces), The Addams Family, Tim Burton themes, The Phantom of the Opera, and many others.</p>\n\n<p>This is more than a concert — it's a Halloween journey through shadow, emotion, and sound. Let yourself be carried away by the magic of gothic music and the warm glow of hundreds of candles.</p>\n\n<style>\n@media screen and (max-width: 600px){iframe{width:100%;}}\n.location-page-temp {display: block!important;}\n</style> \n"
      }
    ],
