        "@value": "Men of the Deeps: 60th Anniversary Christmas Tour"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>The Men of the Deeps, North America's only coal miners' choir, celebrates its sixtieth anniversary with an Ontario Christmas tour. The Cape Breton-based choir will feature a retrospective of its music over the past six decades, as well as new selections from its Diamond Sunset and Christmas recordings.</p>\n\n<p>Website: <a href='https://menofthedeeps.com/' target='_blank'>menofthedeeps.com</a></p>\n\n<style>\n@media screen and (max-width: 600px){\niframe{width:100%;}\n}\n</style>"
      }
