      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>INCLUDES:\n<ul>\n<li> One season ticket seat to all home games of the Collingwood Blues. The Season Ticket holder will have the same seat for every home game, including any home pre-season games</li>\n<li> Choice of seat before individual game tickets go on sale</li>\n<li> One All-Access Pass to the 2026 Cottage Cup</li>\n<li> Access to the VIP founders club lounge to be built at the Eddie Bush Memorial Arena <b><i>(FOUNDERS ONLY)</i></b></li>\n<li> Your name or company name/logo on your seat <b><i>(FOUNDERS ONLY)</i></b></li></ul></p>\n\n<p><b>Early Bird</b> rate (until Apr. 30) | Founders: $623.00, Season: $338.00 (per seat, including all fees)<br>\n<b>Advance</b> rate (until Aug. 30) | Founders: $633.40, Season: $348.40 (per seat, including all fees)<br>\n<b>Regular</b> rate (as of Sept. 1) | Founders: $642.50, Season: $357.50 (per seat, including all fees)</p>\n\n<p>For accessible seating, please contact <a href='mailto:ontario@ticketpro.ca'><b>ontario@ticketpro.ca</b></a>.</p>\n"
