    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "\n\n    <p><span style='color: red;'><b>TWO WORLDS COLLIDE FOR 1 EPIC SHOW!</span><br>TWO Mind Blowing Shows... Three times the fun!</b></p>\n    \n    <p>Feel the roar of the monster trucks as the Monster Madness Tour stops in Medicine Hat Alberta at the Medicine Hat Speedway with stars from the 'FMX World Tour' and more! This is an action-packed afternoon fans won't want to miss!</p>\n    \n    <p><b>MONSTER MADNESS TOUR:</b> Some of the biggest trucks in the world will debut in Medicine Hat, Including Points Leader Alberta's Ruff Neck & Canada's #1 female Monster Truck SABOTAGE. Monster Madness will have you on your feet as you watch the 10,000 pounds of MONSTER TRUCKS soar through the air! The competition will include tricks like wheelies, racing, monster truck freestyle and more!</p>\n    <p><em></b>*Monster Truck lineup subject to change without notice.</em></b></p>\n    <p><b>FMX WORLD TOUR</b> will leave fans and families amazed as death defying stunts only the brave would attempt are performed, inside the arena. FMX World Tour is the perfect blend of athletic ability, extreme stunt competitions and tricks and flips! FMX World Tour stars will be performing such tricks as, captain morgan, kiss of death, cliff hangers, in addition to the famous BACKFLIP!</p>\n    \n<p><b>CONTACT & MORE INFO</b>: <br>For more details, visit <a href='http://www.monstermadnesstour.ca' target='_blank'>www.monstermadnesstour.ca</a> or email <a href='mailto:info@edgeentertainmentgroup.ca'>info@edgeentertainmentgroup.ca</a>.<br>\n<strong>Social Media:</strong> Facebook (<a href='https://www.facebook.com/monstermadnesscanada/' target='_blank'>monstermadnesscanada</a>) | Instagram (<a href='https://www.instagram.com/monstermadnesstourcanada' target='_blank'>@monstermadnesstourcanada</a>)</p>\n    \n    \n\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {display: block!important;}\n.location-event-temp {display: none!important;}\n</style>\n"
      }
