    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasDerivedFrom": [
      {
        "@id": "https://ww2.ticketpro.ca/event.php?event_id=7598"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/url": [
      {
        "@id": "https://ww2.ticketpro.ca/event.php?event_id=7598"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Monster Madness"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p><span style='color: red;'><b>1 MIND-BLOWING SHOW 2:30PM - PIT PARTY 12:30pm - 2:00pm</b></span></p>\n<p>Feel the roar of the monster trucks as the Monster Madness heads to Simco ON.  Three Champions! Racing - Wheelies - Freestyle. Special guests the stars from the 'FMX World Tour' and Power Wheels Kids Demolition.</p>\n\n<p>The MONSTER MADNESS TOUR, featuring some of the biggest MONSTER TRUCKS in the industry, will have you on your feet as you watch 10,000 pounds of a monster truck soaring through the air! The competition will include wheelies, racing, monster truck freestyle and more!  </p>\n\n<p>The FMX WORLD TOUR act will leave fans and families amazed as death defying stunts only the brave would attempt are performed, inside the arena. FMX World Tour is the perfect blend of athletic ability, extreme stunt competitions and tricks and flips! FMX World Tour stars will perform tricks such as, lazy boy, backflips, seat grabs, cliff hangers, in addition to the infamous kiss of death!</p>\n\n<p>Power Wheels - Kids Power Wheels Demolition Derby during intermission. Sign your kids up for this event. </p>\n\n<p><b>PIT PARTY - PIT PARTY 12:30pm -2pm</b> Fans will get a chance to meet the drivers, get up close to the monster trucks, take pictures and receive autographs. </p>\n\n<p><b>MONSTER TRUCK RIDES</b> Monster Truck rides will be available for an additional fee before the show and after the show. True North  Canada's #1 Monster Truck Ride Truck will be in the house to give rides.  </p>\n\n<p><b>VIP TICKETS INCLUDE</b> MONSTER TRUCK RIDE 30min. EARLY ENTRY TO PIT PARTY AND GRANDSTADND TO PICK YOUR BEST SEATS FIRST. FREE EVENT LANYARD & POSTER EARLY.  PLEASE NOTE SEATING IS GENERAL ADMISSION.  </p>\n\n\n    <p><b>Children 2 and under ON LAP ARE FREE<br>\n        Children 12 AND OLDER = ADULT<br>\n        For more details visit: \n        <a href='https://www.facebook.com/monstermadnesstourcanada'>monster-madness-facebook</a> - \n        <a href='https://www.instagram.com/monstermadnesstourcanada'>@monstermadnesstourcanada - Instagram</a><br>\n        <a href='http://www.monstermadnesstour.ca'>www.monstermadnesstour.ca</a> or \n        <a href='mailto:info@edgeentertainmentgroup.ca'>info@edgeentertainmentgroup.ca</a>\n    </p></b>\n\n    <p><strong>TICKET PRICES INCREASE $5.00 per ticket Day of show!</strong></p>\n\n    <p style='font-size: 70%;'><b>(Monster Truck line up subject to change without notice)</b></p>\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {display: block!important;}\n.location-event-temp {display: none!important;}\n</style>"
      }
