    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Stars Come Out 2026 - Theatre by the Bay"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p><b>Theatre by the Bay's Annual Gala Fundraiser <br>\nPresented by Galina Johnston, IG Private Wealth Management </b></p>\n\n\n<p>Evening performance and gala celebration </p>\n \n<p>Perfect for: Theatre supporters, corporate hosts, elegant nights out, arts champions, and anyone who loves Broadway-calibre talent up close. </p>\n \n<p>Where the stars shine for a cause. </p>\n \n<p>Stars Come Out is Theatre by the Bay's signature gala - an unforgettable evening that brings celebrated performers from stage and screen together for a one-night-only theatrical event. </p>\n \n<p>This is not a typical fundraiser. It is a professionally produced cabaret experience featuring powerhouse vocals, dynamic staging, and moments of surprise - all in support of professional theatre in Barrie. </p>\n \n<p>The evening includes a red-carpet atmosphere, live musical performances, and opportunities to support the future of Theatre by the Bay through sponsorship, philanthropy, and community engagement. </p>\n \n<p>Each performance is crafted with the same artistic care and polish as our mainstage productions, creating a night that feels both celebratory and meaningful. </p>\n \n<p>When you attend Stars Come Out, you are doing more than enjoying an extraordinary evening. </p>\n \n<p>You are investing in emerging artists.  <br>\nYou are strengthening cultural life in our city.  <br>\nYou are helping ensure that professional theatre continues to thrive for the next 25 years. </p>\n \n<p>Dress up. Gather your guests. <br>\nBe part of the celebration. </p>\n \n<p><b><i>Seats are limited and this event sells quickly. Reserve early.</b></i></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<style>\n@media screen and (max-width: 600px){\niframe{width:100%;}\n}\n</style>\n"
      }
