      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>The Unfaithful Servants have become one of Canada's must-see acts. Known for explosive instrumentals, soaring harmonies, and powerful songwriting, they deliver a thrilling mix of folk, bluegrass, and Americana. With standout performances at Canada's top festivals, as well as a Canadian Folk Music Award nomination for New Group Of The Year, the Servants are gaining national attention.\n</p>\n\n<style>\n.titleTax {display: none !important;}\n</style>\n"
