        "@value": "Chamber Music Series | Vancouver Chamber Music Society"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>Presented by the Vancouver Chamber Music Society</p>\n\n<p><b>Academy Chamber Players</b>: Monday, October 26, 2026 at 1:00 p.m.<br>\n<b>Yoon, Sarkissian and Pfau</b>: Monday, November 23, 2026 at 1:00 p.m.<br>\n<b>Galvin Cello Quartet</b>: Monday, February 8, 2027 at 1:00 p.m.<br>\n<b>K Stobbe and P Williamson</b>: Monday, March 1, 2027 at 1:00 p.m.<br>\n<b>Academy Chamber Players</b>: Monday, April 5, 2027 at 1:00 p.m.<br>\n<b>Despres, Davis, Raymond & Chan</b>: Monday, May 10, 2027 at 1:00 p.m.</p>\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {display: block!important;}\n@media screen and (max-width: 600px){iframe{width:100%;}}\n</style>\n"
