      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "VaughnCo Entertainment Presents CREEDENCE CLEARWATER ARRIVAL"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p> <b>VaughnCo Entertainment</b>  is proud to present <b>'Creedence Clearwater Arrival'</b>, a powerhouse tribute celebrating the legendary music of Creedence Clearwater Revival — one of America's most influential rock bands. The show authentically recreates the unmistakable sound, driving rhythm, and raw energy that defined CCR during their late-1960s and early-1970s prime.</p>\n\n<p>Built on commanding vocals, tight musicianship, and meticulous attention to detail, The Ultimate CCR Tribute Show delivers a nonstop journey through CCR's greatest hits and fan favorites. From timeless classics like Proud Mary and Bad Moon Rising to iconic anthems such as Fortunate Son, Have You Ever Seen the Rain, and Down on the Corner, audiences are transported back to a golden era of American rock 'n' roll.</p>\n\n<p>Every performance is crafted to capture the spirit, authenticity, and groove that made Creedence Clearwater Revival a cultural phenomenon. Whether appearing in theaters, festivals, casinos, or concert halls, this show brings the music to life with passion, energy, and undeniable crowd connection.</p>\n\n<p>Relive the sound, the soul, and the swagger of classic rock with <b>Creedence Clearwater Arrival</b> — a true concert experience for fans of all generations.</p>\n\n<style>\n@media screen and (max-width: 600px){\niframe{width:100%;}\n}\n</style>"
      }
    ],
